N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 61.2 - Presumption as to existing rates

State Regulations

The rates, rules and regulations relating thereto that are
in effect when the proceeding is initiated will not be presumed to be just and
reasonable. Notes
